{"tid":1046914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個真人真事鬼故","createTime":"2019-03-04T14:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T16:08:13.000Z","uid":96501,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"024bb5c48249c243759bb39184335702f3f6e273","tid":1046914,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我先<br />\n<br />\n話說果陣我仲讀緊中一，<br />\n好記得有個weekend，<br />\n全家人都返咗大陸兩日一夜探親，<br />\n所以得返我一個係屋企。<br />\n<br />\n果晚同學們係msn問我想唔想開多線煲通宵電話粥，<br />\n而果陣仲係未有人人有手提電話嘅年代（至少我未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），<br />\n所以好自然打我屋企電話，<br />\n咁我地就開始傾傾傾傾到淩晨1點。<br />\n<br />\n由於小弟屋企電話係無線果隻，<br />\n所以傾左4個幾鐘已經冇乜電。<br />\n我同佢地講我想拎部電話去差電先，<br />\n轉頭3點再打返俾我。<br />\n如是者我就拎返出廳差電，<br />\n但等等下唔小心瞓著咗。<br />\n<br />\n瞓到濛濛鬆鬆之際電話就響，<br />\n但由於唔想起身所以冇聽，<br />\n而電話響左兩三下就冇響，<br />\n果刻我好好奇點解咁快cut線，<br />\n但由於太眼訓所以冇理。<br />\n<br />\n去到星期一返學，<br />\n啲同學問我做乜咁冇雷瞓咗，又話傾電話之類。<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「唔係啊因為沖緊涼聽唔到電話」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「唔係喎有人聽然後話你瞓左㗎喎？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「下，冇理由，果晚我屋企都冇人，你地係咪打錯電話？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「應該冇喎，對方一拎起個電話係個男人聽，我地仲問：唔該我想揾（小弟全朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）吖，對方就答你已經瞓左，我地先收線嘅」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後睇返同學個來電顯示，又真係冇打錯，<br />\n我再問屋企人係咪有人set左飛線之類，全部人話冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟個男人係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解又會知我瞓左教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：真人真事"},{"pid":"8d64e4e72774d7346df649286e9ca851fc572fa8","tid":1046914,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"你篇屄文唔好再長啲？"},{"pid":"beab7037d541e1b3c26df7f5ee21294114d60dfd","tid":1046914,"uid":96501,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8d64e4e72774d7346df649286e9ca851fc572fa8","tid":1046914,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"你篇屄文唔好再長啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"來龍去脈要講清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f36e4da80d3dffcdf2cc6f072abbba7ec0e59ab","tid":1046914,"uid":236918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:12:03.000Z","msg":"做醫院追更訓宿舍<br />\n點知由5點癱到天黑都未訓得著<br />\n睇睇電話顯示: 8:10分<br />\n然後一轉身<br />\n床邊企撚左個女人(個樣灰灰地一睇就知唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n我未黎得切反應佢已經壓住我<br />\n我好撚驚全身郁唔到<br />\n當時係合埋眼同想用全力起身都唔得<br />\n然後我做左件好後悔既事就係擘大眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到個女人面對面係正我上面<br />\n仲要微笑(好撚陰森個種笑法)<br />\n然後伸條脷出黎，好記得條脷係尖尖地好紅既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個下我用盡全身力一野彈到起身<br />\n鞋都無著頭也不回跑出房<br />\n之後喊到仆街咁去塭同事幫我去拎返d私人物品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86091924a4fce6e9a4d1088b3c8e2fa27ea820ee","tid":1046914,"uid":201061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"又話瞓著<br />\n又話沖涼聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08608643b28f61e909dcd6fb51b5ff7d9b63127c","tid":1046914,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86091924a4fce6e9a4d1088b3c8e2fa27ea820ee","tid":1046914,"uid":201061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"又話瞓著<br />\n又話沖涼聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:17:03.000Z","msg":"果陣唔想俾人知我冇雷訓咗嘅大話嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b473f6b3574afded139b435d49af0df6fa506e","tid":1046914,"uid":201061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08608643b28f61e909dcd6fb51b5ff7d9b63127c","tid":1046914,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86091924a4fce6e9a4d1088b3c8e2fa27ea820ee","tid":1046914,"uid":201061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"又話瞓著<br />\n又話沖涼聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:17:03.000Z","msg":"果陣唔想俾人知我冇雷訓咗嘅大話嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157dda622df98503413da26c306fb1adc7aa8c29","tid":1046914,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86091924a4fce6e9a4d1088b3c8e2fa27ea820ee","tid":1046914,"uid":201061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"又話瞓著<br />\n又話沖涼聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:12:59.000Z","msg":"佢唔想啲同學知佢訓左姐<br />\n好難估/明咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b898d54ed3a2bf4020c8de2ba2fbf1ac539af5c6","tid":1046914,